;
; Module function description  
"<MODULEFUNCTION>" ;<!-- short overview documentation of module function; add reference to detailed information, if available-->
"	<General>	"
"	MM Customized is a collection of prepared spare items for individual adoptions. "
"	</General>	"
""
"	<F1 Name='Analog Inputs and Outputs' LastModified='4.0.0.0'>"
"	Predefined Channels (CustAnaIn[]) for plant specific purpose, usage defined hardcodede at time of sw generation.	"
"   Last Update: Separation of unchangeable code parts of tasks ran_def and MsgCU into new tasks in Cust_Internals"
"	</F1>"
"	<F2 Name='Digital Inputs and Outputs'  LastModified='4.0.0.0'>"
"	Predefined Channels (CustDigIn[]) for plant specific purpose, usage defined hardcodede at time of sw generation.	"
"	</F2>"
"	<F3 Name='Customizable controllers'  LastModified='4.0.0.0'>"
"	8 predefined PID- Controllers for plant specific purpose, usage defined hardcodede at time of sw generation.	"
"	</F3>"
"	<F4 Name='Customer Inputs and Outputs'  LastModified='4.0.0.0'>"
"	Prepared channels with highly parameter definable function for changeable Inputs and Outputs (CustomerIO), without hardcodeded purpose at time of sw generation.	"
"	</F4>"
"	<F5 Name='Customer Messages'  LastModified='4.2.2.0'>"
"	Additional 300 Messages prepared for : Alarms 1601-1700, Warnings 1701-1800, Operating messages 3601-3700, IN Interface cleanup	"
"	</F5>"
"	<F6 Name='Customer Counters'  LastModified='4.2.2.0'>"
"	New OUT Interface rCA_PI_Dur_COffset for custom PI duration offset "
"	10 Customizable Counters, stored in permanent memory file (last change 2015-02-04)	"
"	</F7>"
"	<F7 Name='Customizable Scaling Blocks'  LastModified='4.11.0.0'>"
"	10 predefined linear scaling blocks for plant specific purpose, usage defined hardcodede at time of sw generation.	"
"	</F7>"
""
"	<Info>"
"	This module is also the prefered place, where tasks to perform plant specific programmed functions are to be implemented.	"
